# AgriHub Fertigation — watchdog cron (the independent safety net).
# Install with:  crontab -e   (then paste the line below, adjusting paths)
#
# Runs every minute. The watchdog reads the root .env itself (so CONTROL_APP_URL
# and DB_PATH come from there); the explicit CONTROL_APP_URL below is just a
# safety override. Use the venv's python so scikit-fuzzy/requests are available.

* * * * * /home/fadelaryap/agrihub-fertigation/.venv/bin/python /home/fadelaryap/agrihub-fertigation/watchdog/watchdog.py >> /home/fadelaryap/agrihub-fertigation/watchdog/watchdog.log 2>&1

# Notes:
#  - The Control App scheduler (07:00 & 16:00, editable in the UI) is SEPARATE and
#    lives inside the Next.js process — it is NOT in cron. Only the watchdog is.
#  - The daily "new day" Telegram digest (00:00 WIB) also runs inside that same
#    Next.js scheduler (spawns `brain.py --digest`) — likewise NOT in cron.
#  - Logrotate suggestion for watchdog.log (optional):
#      /home/fadelaryap/agrihub-fertigation/watchdog/watchdog.log {
#        weekly; rotate 4; compress; missingok; notifempty; copytruncate;
#      }
